summary:
=== Purchase Information === Product Title: Ochine Electric Heated Eyelash Curler Long Lasting Eye Lash Perm Heated Roll Makeup Tool Review Date: 2019/10/14 Store: Ochine Average Rating: 3.2 Product Details: {'Package Dimensions': '7.4 x 3.3 x 0.1 inches; 0.81 Ounces'} Review Text: Heats more than expected but doesn't burn or hurt. You have to carefully make sure the lashes are straight and not going the wrong way or they will stay that way. Best idea is use a regular curler and set the curl with this. Handy little tool. Glad I bought it. Won't use it everyday, just special occasions. Review Title: Neat little tool Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: 4D Silk Fiber Lash Mascara, Waterproof Mascara 180 Degree Flexible Brush Curling Lashes,Natural Thickening and Lengthening Mascara Review Date: 2020/01/01 Store: Blue Finger Average Rating: 3.2 Product Details: {'Special Feature': 'Waterproof', 'Brand': 'Blue Finger', 'Specialty': 'Waterproof', 'Unit Count': '1.0 Ounce', 'Package Information': 'Tube', 'Package Dimensions': '4.7 x 1.3 x 1 inches; 0.81 Ounces'} Review Text: This mascara was a big surprise. It performs like a very expensive mascara at a drugstore price. No smudging, flaking or clumping. Washes off with pure water and a bit of rubbing. Add some cleanser and it's effortless to remove. I can fall asleep with it on and no black eyes in the morning, just a few flakes from sleeping. It offers full volume and lengthens well. If you use a curler, you can get a very dramatic effect. It's buildable for more false eyelash looks without being clumpy. The wand is not straight. It is like a smiley face curve. But with a twist of the end, it curves into a "u" shape to get different angles. I would love this even with a normal straight brush.
The only complaint is that it dries out faster than others I've used, but is about the same as tarte waterproof in this regard. My favorite mascara so far! I will be ordering extras in case it's discontinued. Review Title: Yes To This One Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: MOSTORY Cloud Volume Lash Mascara Black - Lash Mascara Black Volume Length Smudgeproof Curl Eyelash Lifted Thick Long Lasting Volumious 4D Silk No Flicks No Clumps Bristle Brush (0.3 oz) Review Date: 2020/09/20 Store: MOSTORY Average Rating: 4.1 Product Details: {'Product Benefits': 'Long Lasting, Curling', 'Special Feature': 'Smudge Proof', 'Brand': 'MOSTORY', 'Item Form': 'OIL', 'Number of Items': '1', 'Package Dimensions': '4.96 x 1.1 x 1.06 inches; 1.45 Ounces'} Review Text: Did not like. It added thickness and darkened my lashes. But it was really clumpy. It went on like a mousse, kind of fluffy. I think thats what made it clump. It also clumped the lashes together besides leaving balls of mascara clumps on the lashes. I hoped for better based on the reviews, but it didn't go on nicely at all. It was sweatproof, yet it did smear over night just a bit. Honestly, it looked exactly the same in the morning as it did when I first applied it, besides the slight smudge under one eye. So I have to say, that's pretty bad to look like you slept in your mascara when it's been freshly applied. Big thumbs down on this one. Review Title: Not for me Rating: 1.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: 4D Silk Fiber Lash Mascara Black, Natural Waterproof Mascara Extra Long Lash,Thick Thickening and Lengthening, No Clumping, No Smudging, Lasting Voluminous Eyelashes Dramatic Extension Mascara Review Date: 2021/04/13 Store: SIKEMAY Average Rating: 4.0 Product Details: {'Color': 'Black', 'Special Feature': 'Smudge Proof, Non Clumping', 'Brand': 'SIKEMAY', 'Specialty': 'Waterproof, Hypoallergenic', 'Unit Count': '1.00 Count', 'Package Dimensions': '8.9 x 4 x 1.1 inches; 2.57 Ounces', 'UPC': '764690676852', 'Manufacturer': 'SIKEMAY'} Review Text: This had a super strong chemical smell. It looked nice with one coat. No thickness or volume but it lengthened ok. However it did dry super fast and adding a second coat was a terrible idea. It clumped into a sticky mess. One coat wasn't enough volume for me. It was hard to remove, I had to use castor oil. Pass on this one. Review Title: Hard to remove and only use one coat or it will glue up on you. Rating: 2.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Natural Waterproof Lash Mascara Black, 4D Silk Fiber Eyelash Mascara Makeup, Lengthening and Thick, No Clumping, Smudge-proof, Long-Lasting Voluminous Eyelashes Dramatic Extension Makeup Kit Eye Lash Review Date: 2021/04/13 Store: SIKEMAY Average Rating: 4.1 Product Details: {'Color': 'black', 'Brand': 'SIKEMAY', 'Item Form': 'Cream', 'Number of Items': '1', 'Unit Count': '1.00 Count', 'Package Dimensions': '7.2 x 4 x 1.2 inches; 2.4 Ounces', 'UPC': '764690676845', 'Manufacturer': 'SIKEMAY'} Review Text: With one coat, this looked pretty good. It gave pretty nice length. Not much volume. You can't do more than one coat though, cause it makes your lashes stick together really badly and you have to remove it and start again. It's super hard to remove, you need petroleum jelly, baby oil or olive oil. Something heavy duty. I need more volume and it was just messy to work with. It also smelled strongly of chemicals. Review Title: Nice length, but no volume. Rating: 3.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: 4D Silk Fiber Lash Mascara Black, Waterproof Natural Thick Fiber Mascara, Thick Thickening Lengthening, Dramatic Extension Voluminous Eyelashes Mascara, No Clumping, No Smudging Lasting All Day Review Date: 2021/04/13 Store: SIKEMAY Average Rating: 4.0 Product Details: {'Color': 'black', 'Special Feature': 'Water, Smudge Proof, Non Clumping', 'Brand': 'SIKEMAY', 'Specialty': 'Waterproof, hypoallergenic', 'Unit Count': '1.00 Count', 'Package Dimensions': '7.2 x 4 x 1.1 inches; 2.4 Ounces', 'UPC': '764690676838', 'Manufacturer': 'SIKEMAY'} Review Text: So this smelled strongly of chemicals. It was easy enough to remove with soap and water, then face cleanser. It didn't smudge overnight. One coat looked nice, gave decent length but no volume or thickness. Beware of the second coat. It will clump up and make your lashes stick together like glue. Awful. If you want a simple one coat mascara for everyday and can deal with the smell, this will be nice. But I can find better. And the smell turned my stomach. Kinda scared me. Review Title: Smelled bad. Don't use two coats. Rating: 2.0 --------------------------------------------------

SUMMARY:
The analysis reveals a clear preference for effective and user-friendly makeup tools, particularly mascara. The individual exhibits a pattern of seeking products that enhance lash appearance through curling and volumizing effects, with a notable focus on waterproof features. Ratings indicate a significant appreciation for products that provide dramatic results, particularly those that lengthen without clumping, as seen in high ratings for some mascara purchases.

Consistent complaints about clumping, chemical smells, and difficulty in removal suggest a low tolerance for mascara that performs poorly in these areas. This user values products that offer performance comparable to high-end options but at a reasonable price, showcasing sensitivity to value for money. The inclination towards special occasion use rather than daily application signals a preference for versatility in makeup tools, favoring products that can achieve professional looks with ease.

Overall, the core preferences reflect a desire for efficacy, ease of use, and reliability in performance, steering clear of products that do not uphold these standards, while also demonstrating a cautionary approach to trying new items influenced by prior experiences.

target_interaction.title: Wouldn't recommend
target_interaction.text: Did not care for this mascara. Although it was smudge proof and easy to remove, it was clumpy with two coats and my lashes stuck together. With one coat it wasn't very impressive. No lift or length. Decent separation but no volume. Nothing special. Would not recommend.
